 (其實無吹奏得咁好食)<br />\n<br />\n肉? 炸豬扒果D? 高田馬場間炸豬超好食<br />\n<br />\n你可以上TABELOG望望, 3.8分以上可以去馬<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GzfbXtQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGzfbXtQ.png&h=dd2bba79&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"daffa2784b7847800e993f02a2a28110a0d967d2","tid":1284153,"uid":18484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"落仙台玩好過啦"},{"pid":"adaca28ffa4680688ff74d9ba7147dae1c6a5f9d","tid":1284153,"uid":230659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"daffa2784b7847800e993f02a2a28110a0d967d2","tid":1284153,"uid":18484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"落仙台玩好過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:13:12.000Z","msg":"ching仙台有冇咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c8c79053eeca7ff87e55bf8886e5419fd20da3","tid":1284153,"uid":178800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:13:42.000Z","msg":"秋田<br />\n可以去男鹿半島<br />\n認識一下當地傳統習俗<br />\n返東京途中可去仙台食最出名既牛舌<br />\n如果你唔驚,經過福島可以逗留一陣<br />\n車站旁邊就有個地震館之類的博物館,了解一下,<br />\n再唔驚D,可以買下當地食物,支持下,<br />\n利申: 我當年買左盒牛奶,無事,生存到而家"},{"pid":"26ca1dc00b79ebc3caf21788b3f4a626b0a1ed95","tid":1284153,"uid":45357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"秋田 去過田澤湖同角館<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n田澤湖都係坐觀光巴士睇下風景<br />\n角館就係d古代武士街<br />\n<br />\n但日本東北我覺得都係青森吸引d"},{"pid":"0429a28ff72f4bf11f5d9e2367cbe6f76d2147c6","tid":1284153,"uid":45357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26ca1dc00b79ebc3caf21788b3f4a626b0a1ed95","tid":1284153,"uid":45357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"秋田 去過田澤湖同角館<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n田澤湖都係坐觀光巴士睇下風景<br />\n角館就係d古代武士街<br />\n<br />\n但日本東北我覺得都係青森吸引d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"